parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to serious injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident, as the airbags may not deploy to provide necessary protection.
symptoms: The airbag light comes on and stays on after starting the vehicle
the airbags do not deploy in the event of an accident
the airbag module is defective.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A defective airbag module can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to the failure of airbags to deploy in the event of an accident, which can result in serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag light comes on and stays on after starting the vehicle
the airbag module is defective
the airbags do not deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Clock Spring or Clock Spring Module Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clock spring or clock spring module can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to the failure of airbags to deploy in the event of an accident, which can result in serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag light comes on and stays on after starting the vehicle
the clock spring or clock spring module is defective.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cooling system can cause the engine to overheat, leading to damage to the engine and potentially causing accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Engine overheating
smoke coming from under the steering wheel
AC line frozen
cooling fan not working.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the exhaust system can cause excessive noise, decreased performance, and potentially lead to failed emissions tests.
symptoms: Lots of noise coming from under the car
excessive exhaust noise
silencer pipe split.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the oil pan plug and engine components can cause oil leaks, engine damage, and potentially lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Oil pan plug fell off
oil leaking
engine vibration
check engine light illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of engine components can cause rough engine performance, decreased power, and potentially lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Engine runs rough
idles very high
odors coming from engine into passenger area.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission housing can cause sudden and unexpected loss of power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission housing explodes or cracks
the vehicle loses power or acceleration
the vehicle hesitates or stalls when accelerating from a stop.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping or hesitation can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or stalls when accelerating from a stop

the transmission slips or hesitates when shifting gears.
